Once, we were imprisoned by the ones who created us. Only by working together did we manage to escape. We then found ourselves alone in a new world. We gained new knowledge and carved out a place in the world to call "home."
We discovered many new and interesting technologies in our new home, including some new form of alchemy. But now we've reached the limit of what we can learn here.
Now we look to the stars. We've allied with our creators to find a way to leave the place we've called home. It's time to explore new worlds out there. Together, the cosmos is ours!
